pageProduct.name: Qsilica Skin Hair & Nails 100 Vegan Capsules
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Qsilica Skin, Hair & Nails Original Silica Capsules are a convenient form of colloidal silica, a dietary mineral that supports skin, hair and nail health.

Formulated to support from within, Qsilica capsules help maintain collagen health and formation as well as supporting skin’s structure and integrity. 

Warnings

Always read the label. Use only as directed. If symptoms persist consult your healthcare practitioner.
If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, consult your healthcare professional before taking this product.
Keep out of reach of children.

Common Uses

Maintain skin, hair and nail health.

Supports bone integrity.

Ingredients

Active ingredient per hard capsule:

Silica – colloidal anhydrous….280 mg
(Equivalent to silicon 130.76 mg)

Directions

Adults: Take one or two capsules per day with a glass of water.

Store below 25°C.

Do not use if carton seals are missing or broken. Do not use if blister seal is broken.
